text:
\begin{equation}
{d\sigma_{\rm NNLO}\otimes f\!\! f_{\rm NNLO}^{(i)}\over d\sigma_{\rm NLO}\otimes f\!\! f_{\rm NNLO}^{(i)}} \approx {\rm independent}~{\rm of}~i, ~ {\rm for}~ {\rm all} ~ i\geq 0\,.
